OL,3,CD-Day veteran Stan Ford dies at 100
OL,5,FD-Day veteran Stan Ford from Bath has
OL,6,Fdied at the age of 100.
OL,8,FHe was serving on board the HMS
OL,9,FFratton when it sunk in 1944 with the
OL,10,Floss of 31 crew.
OL,12,FStan would later become an ambassador
OL,13,Ffor the British Normandy Memorial and
OL,14,Fwas chosen to take part in the Queen's
OL,15,Fbaton relay ahead of the Commonwealth
OL,16,Fgames in 2022.
OL,18,FThe Normandy Memorial Trust said it
OL,19,Fwas "deeply saddened".
