OL,5,FThey said "We were so fortunate that
OL,6,Fhe visited the memorial multiple
OL,7,Ftimes, all thanks to the support of
OL,8,FSpirit of Normandy Trust
OL,10,F"He dedicated himself to keeping alive
OL,11,Fthe memory of his fallen comrades and
OL,12,Fwas a true friend of the memorial.
OL,13,FStan, we will miss you."
OL,15,FSpeaking to ITV in 2023 as part the D-
OL,16,FDay 80 commemorations, Stan described
OL,17,Fhis time on the HMS Fratton and his
OL,18,Finvolvement in D-Day.
