OL,5,F"The gun and the platform went on down
OL,6,Fand I swam around a bit, came to.
OL,7,FThere were lots of voices around."
OL,9,F"We lost 31 of the crew. They didn't
OL,10,Fsurvive. They had a complement of
OL,11,Fabout 80.
OL,13,F"I was saying 'My back, my back' and I
OL,14,Fwas being pulled aboard. Immediately
OL,15,Fnature put me to sleep, that's my
OL,16,Fwords. And I was unconscious.
OL,18,F"And I woke up in 84th British Field
OL,19,FHospital."
