OL,3,CD-Day veteran Stan Ford dies at 100
OL,5,FMr Ford continued to suffer from his
OL,6,Finjuries - a fractured spine and
OL,7,Finjuries to both legs meant he had to
OL,8,Fwear callipers - but said it was
OL,9,Fsomething he had gotten used to.
OL,11,FStan regularly returned to France to
OL,12,Fhonour fallen soldiers as an
OL,13,Fambassador for the British Normandy
OL,14,FMemorial.
OL,16,FHe also help to raise funds for an
OL,17,Feducation centre on the site of the
OL,18,Fmemorial.
