OL,5,FThe Veteran's Charity were among those
OL,6,Fpaying tribute to Stan. They said "We
OL,7,Fare very sad to learn of the passing
OL,8,Fof Royal Navy D-Day Veteran, Stan Ford.
OL,10,F"Rest peacefully dear Stan. Thank you
OL,11,Ffor your life of remarkable service."
